name: Maxrosenbaum.GitHub.io
body:
### Welcome To My Github Page!
I am currently a junior at Lehigh University. I am working on a major in Journalism and a double minor in Psychology and Creative Writing. 

If you would like to see a more comprehensive display of my work in both journalism and photography, please visit [My Website](http://www.maxlrosenbaum.com/)

### Some examples of my work with Data Visualization
Throughout the course of the semester, I have been taking a class in Data Visualization. I have since mastered many techniques that have allowed me to visually display information.

**Examples:**

* [A Map of My Favorite Restaurants in Nassau County, Long Island](MaxRosenbaum.github.io/map.html)
* [A Timeline of Green Day's Discography](MaxRosenbaum.github.io/GreenDay.html)
* [An Infographic About The Distribution of Lehigh Students Per College](https://maxrosenbaum.github.io/colleges.html)
* [A Line Graph of Lehigh Enrollment Per College](MaxRosenbaum.github.io/lehighcolleges.html)
* [A Map of U.S Green Day Concerts in the 2010's](MaxRosenbaum.github.io/GreenDayConcerts.html) 

### My Work With Social Media 

As a journalist, I always try and stay updated with social media. It **is** the future. Here are some of my social media platforms/accounts: 

* [My Photography Facebook Page](https://www.facebook.com/MaxRosenbaumPhotos/?ref=aymt_homepage_panel)
* [My Photography Instagram](https://www.instagram.com/maxlaurenphotos/)
* [Tumblr](http://maxielauren.tumblr.com/)
* [Flickr](https://www.flickr.com/photos/maxielauren)
* [Twitter](https://twitter.com/maxielaurenbaum?lang=en)
